Class Viewer

  • java.lang.Object
    • Viewer

  • public class Viewer
extends java.lang.Object
    A Viewer manages the forms. A Viewer sends forms to a CSVDatei. A Viewer gets forms from a CSVDatei.
    Author:
    Philippe Krüttli
